g.text: Read a tab separated csv file
Quality control, trim and clip each forward and reverse RNA-Seq fastQ paired dataset with FastQC and the
RawReadManipulator. Each dataset pair is mapped to a supplied reference transcriptome using bowtie2. The Java
snippet then uses samtools to convert the sam file to bam, sort, index and extract read counts from the bam file.
